      "coverage": "gaps",
      "gaps": [
        "No per-downstream-service latency histogram (e.g., enrichment_downstream_duration{service=inventory}). Cannot isolate which dependency is causing slowdowns.",
        "No metric for upstream timeouts / abandoned requests — the service may report 'success' for enrichments that the caller already gave up on",
        "No metric for downstream error rates broken out by service",
        "No in-flight / concurrent request gauge to detect saturation"
      ]
    },
    "tracing": {
      "coverage": "missing",
      "gaps": [
        "No distributed tracing mentioned. Request ID in logs is a start, but without trace propagation (e.g., OpenTelemetry spans), correlating a slow enrichment to a specific downstream call across service boundaries requires manual log grep.",
