      ]
    },
    "debugging_capability": "Moderate. Structured JSON logging with request ID and per-call duration is a solid foundation. However, the 3am engineer will struggle to answer 'why are enrichments timing out?' without per-service latency histograms and distributed traces. They will need to grep logs by request ID and manually sum durations."
